ical Male And Womanpic.twitter.com/dyJG1iuJ8S \\\"I could not imagine getting inside the ring with a biological man,\\\" shields noted, adding \\\"Even though I sparred against a man, but fighting for the Olympics is way bigger than that and so much more on the line to have to go with an opposite gender.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Just Unfair\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"Two-Time Gold Medalist Reacts\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"'Scary' Olympic Boxing Match\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"Biological Male\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"Womanpic.twitter.com/dyJG1iuJ8S\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"a biological man\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"shields\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"an opposite gender\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women fight against women and men fight against men.\\\"\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shields urged that Khelif is \\\"much bigger and stronger and it is scary,\\\" adding \\\"when you are born with bigger muscles and neck and you have grown up to be a man.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shields\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger muscles\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"neck\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, he did not change genders when he was a kid.\\\"\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genders\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, it is, to me, it is just unfair and I just can not believe that it is being done and I just could not imagine it happening to me,\\\" the Olympian further stated.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999994720383, \"rank\": 5.278077857281001e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was previously disqualified from the 2023 Women's World Boxing Championships by the International Boxing Association (IBA) owing to the fact that he was \\\"found to have competitive advantages over other female competitors,\\\" astatementby the IBA notes.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.233942783692517e-32, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9428916298822508, \"rank\": 0.060564923068274296, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9428916298822508, \"rank\": 0.060564923068274296, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 Women's World Boxing Championships\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive advantages\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"other female competitors\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisation also warned that the Olympic committee is guilty of \\\"inconsistent application of eligibility criteria\\\" which is a threat to \\\"competitive fairness and athletes' safety.\\\"\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organisation\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic committee\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"inconsistent application\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"eligibility criteria\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"a threat\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive fairness\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' safety\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shields added \\\"It is very hard to qualify for the Olympics, you have to go through so many different international tournaments, country tournaments, to even make it to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shields\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"so many different international tournaments\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"country tournaments\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, for me, I can understand her devastation but it should not be ruined due to a man and I think that the Olympics definitely dropped the ball, you know.\\\"\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her devastation\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not have anything against transgender women or transgender men,\\\" Shields further explained.\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender women\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender men\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"Shields\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adding \\\"All I am saying is men should fight against men, women should fight against women and transgenders should fight against transgenders.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"transgenders\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"transgenders\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is how I fell, I will stand with that.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not homophobic or anything like that or against the gay community, but that's not right.\\\"\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3078}, {\"ngram\": \"the gay community\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another Olympian, Australia's boxing captain Caitlin Parker has also spoken out against the men in women's boxing.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999994720383, \"rank\": 5.278077857281001e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3161, \"end\": 3170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9502894803148216, \"rank\": 0.041148386957930314, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3188, \"end\": 3202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Parker\", \"score\": 0.9999997772802337, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Parker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Parker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Parker\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's boxing captain Caitlin Parker is the first Olympic athlete to speak out against the men in women's boxing.She says, \\\"I do not agree with them being allowed to compete in sport, especially combat sports.\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9502894803148216, \"rank\": 0.041148386957930314, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q2